title: Children in Gaza ‘dying and fainting in the streets from hunger’
description: At least 83 more people were killed in Israeli attacks over the last day as Israel’s devastating war on Gaza entered its sixth month.

title: Gaza tragedy highlights nature of arrogant countries: Ayatollah Khamenei
description: In a meeting with the chairman and members of the Assembly of Experts on Thursday, Ayatollah Ali Khamenei, Leader of the Islamic Revolution, explained the logic behind the Islamic Republic's opposition to the front of arrogance.

title: Iran into 2024 Asian Age Group Championship semis
description: TEHRAN – Iran defeated Singapore 19-8 on Thursday at the 2024 Asian Age Group Championship.
